        {
            "id": "task_7",
            "title": "1.07: Getallen",
            "instruction": "<div class=\"wysiwyg-section-lezen my-3\">\n<div class=\"font-semibold flex items-center gap-2 mb-1 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm select-none\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-eye text-sky-400\"></i> Lezen:</div>\n<ol><li><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">Er zijn verschillende numerieke datatypes binnen Python. De belangrijkste twee zijn:<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">- </span><b style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">Integers</b><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">, dit zijn gehele getallen. Bijvoorbeeld: </span><code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\">5</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">, </span><code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\">45</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">, of </span><code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\">-45</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">.<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">- </span><b style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">Floats</b><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">, dit zijn komma getallen (die schrijf je met een punt!). Bijvoorbeeld </span><code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\">3.4</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">, </span><code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\">1.3</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\"> of </span><code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\">3.142</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">.</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\">Afhankelijk van wat je opslaat wordt dus het datatype bepaald. </span><code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\">rekening</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\"> is dus een float en </span><code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\">aantal_personen</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\"> en </span><code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\">temperatuur</code><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 65, 85); font-size: 0.875rem;\"> zijn integers.</span></li></ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"wysiwyg-section-bewerken my-3\">\n<div class=\"font-semibold flex items-center gap-2 mb-1 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 text-sm select-none\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-pen-to-square text-amber-400\"></i> Bewerken:</div>\n<ol class=\"list-decimal pl-6 space-y-1 mt-1 mb-2\">\n  <li>Declareer een nieuwe variabele met de naam <code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\">tafel_nummer</code>&nbsp;en geef die de waarde \"<code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\"><code class=\"bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs\">41</code></code>\".</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n",
            "files": [
                {
                    "filename": "main.py",
                    "initialCode": "rekening = 34.12 \naantal_personen = 4\ntemperatuur = -3",
                    "isMain": true
